  "detailed_description": "Video games let us take on the role of great generals, brave adventurers or cunning agents.<br>This game, on the other hand, lets you slip into the skin of an alcoholic brown bear whose only goal is to get wasted at any cost.<br>Make sure you have an unforgettable kid's birthday party in this surprising dad simulator and find all the hidden beer bottles. <br><br>A tool tailor-made to confront your childhood traumas and at the same time adequately prepare young parents for their role as guardians.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>lovely, colorful, hand-made graphics<br></li><li>exhilarating music<br></li><li>invigorating gameplay</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609090/extras/80806040a03f142e823aaf89325ad89d.avif?t=1709765051\" width=640 height=352 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609090/extras/401355f15ea8d4f411c1a7cdbe047e42.avif?t=1709765051\" width=640 height=352 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609090/extras/43efb7c7d289528269503917d7b56d33.avif?t=1709765051\" width=640 height=352 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609090/extras/fe051d6018a6dee8dd8d8397513859ec.avif?t=1709765051\" width=640 height=352 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609090/extras/c4b1e0836ac3a5b2096d6becf4a4da49.avif?t=1709765051\" width=640 height=352 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Video games let us take on the role of great generals, brave adventurers or cunning agents.<br>This game, on the other hand, lets you slip into the skin of an alcoholic brown bear whose only goal is to get wasted at any cost.<br>Make sure you have an unforgettable kid's birthday party in this surprising dad simulator and find all the hidden beer bottles. <br><br>A tool tailor-made to confront your childhood traumas and at the same time adequately prepare young parents for their role as guardians.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>lovely, colorful, hand-made graphics<br></li><li>exhilarating music<br></li><li>invigorating gameplay</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609090/extras/80806040a03f142e823aaf89325ad89d.avif?t=1709765051\" width=640 height=352 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609090/extras/401355f15ea8d4f411c1a7cdbe047e42.avif?t=1709765051\" width=640 height=352 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609090/extras/43efb7c7d289528269503917d7b56d33.avif?t=1709765051\" width=640 height=352 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609090/extras/fe051d6018a6dee8dd8d8397513859ec.avif?t=1709765051\" width=640 height=352 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1609090/extras/c4b1e0836ac3a5b2096d6becf4a4da49.avif?t=1709765051\" width=640 height=352 /></span>",
